While your friends revel in the sleek new look, youll enjoy the added improvements that better fit your lifestyle. The redesigned chest is now large enough to hold up to 100 cans. As you enjoy that cold beverage, relax on the Have-A-Seat Lid that supports up to 250 lbs. Four molded cup holders help prevent spills, and the No Crush Comfort Handles offer up a pinch-free grip on the sides. Inside the coolers walls, extra ThermOZONE Insulation holds the cold for five days in temperatures up to 90 degrees F, and still performs amazingly on hotter days. The foam is also free from CFCs, HFCs and HCFCs, which deplete the ozone. When the fun is done, the retextured EZ-Clean top makes washing your cooler easy, and the rustproof, tilted channel makes draining the excess water as simple as opening the attached plug.Coleman 70 Quart Xtreme Light Blue/White Cooler 3000002012

Condition : This item is brand new, unopened and sealed in its original factory box.
